d":"487e198d692891393b7968468e4e3de56ed973be","tid":401394,"uid":41655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:10:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://www.calculushumor.com/uploads/1/2/0/2/12023481/798083717.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.calculushumor.com%2Fuploads%2F1%2F2%2F0%2F2%2F12023481%2F798083717.png&h=c3286bce&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n數學係科學之母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係，數學只係描述科學既工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁冇數學邊有科學啊"},{"pid":"b8b575ab777386ae540e63fa00a97846f6a4ba13","tid":401394,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:16:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://www.calculushumor.com/uploads/1/2/0/2/12023481/798083717.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.calculushumor.com%2Fuploads%2F1%2F2%2F0%2F2%2F12023481%2F798083717.png&h=c3286bce&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n數學係科學之母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係，數學只係描述科學既工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你數學學唔好<br />\n係咪會影響你理解科學呀？"},{"pid":"79fb78b779a88b73f8d949b50206051e157486d4","tid":401394,"uid":34892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:22:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://www.calculushumor.com/uploads/1/2/0/2/12023481/798083717.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.calculushumor.com%2Fuploads%2F1%2F2%2F0%2F2%2F12023481%2F798083717.png&h=c3286bce&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n數學係科學之母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係，數學只係描述科學既工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你數學學唔好<br />\n係咪會影響你理解科學呀？</blockquote><br />\n科研數學唔好，會影響科研質素，有錯嘅結論，大眾理解嘅嘢最後可能係錯嘅。<br />\n班experimentalist濫用p-value做推論就係其中一個例子。"},{"pid":"aa6b26fba77600b20896470da4fbc97b84cd8c32","tid":401394,"uid":34892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:24:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://www.calculushumor.com/uploads/1/2/0/2/12023481/798083717.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.calculushumor.com%2Fuploads%2F1%2F2%2F0%2F2%2F12023481%2F798083717.png&h=c3286bce&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n數學係科學之母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係，數學只係描述科學既工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你數學學唔好<br />\n係咪會影響你理解科學呀？</blockquote><br />\n科研數學唔好，會影響科研質素，有錯嘅結論，大眾理解嘅嘢最後可能係錯嘅。<br />\n班experimentalist濫用p-value做推論就係其中一個例子。</blockquote><br />\nReference: An error made in 1925 led to a crisis in modern science&mdash;now researchers are joining to fix it <a href=\"https://qz.com/1055287/an-error-made-in-1925-led-to-a-crisis-in-modern-science-now-researchers-are-joining-to-fix-it/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqz.com%2F1055287%2Fan-error-made-in-1925-led-to-a-crisis-in-modern-science-now-researchers-are-joining-to-fix-it%2F&d=VDZ0rhTfcdrDQN359Iz3Hcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=949d99c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://qz.com/1055287/an-error-made-in-1925-led-to-a-crisis-in-modern-science-now-researchers-are-joining-to-fix-it/</a>"},{"pid":"138de3f60468d3bf693117b560851c4075155fbf","tid":401394,"uid":133865,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:40:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://www.calculushumor.com/uploads/1/2/0/2/12023481/798083717.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.calculushumor.com%2Fuploads%2F1%2F2%2F0%2F2%2F12023481%2F798083717.png&h=c3286bce&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n數學係科學之母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係，數學只係描述科學既工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁冇數學邊有科學啊</blockquote><br />\n冇數學絕對有科學，科學係描述緊現實世界，就算冇數學存在都可以做到<br />\n當然，我認同數學對科學係好重要，因為佢提供左一種方法去幫我地描述現實世界，現代科學亦離唔開數學<br />\n但唔代表數學係科學之母，更唔代表冇數學就冇科學"},{"pid":"2f3e0ba34d85fc23de7528306f7c8b0919408a09","tid":401394,"uid":133865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:40:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://www.calculushumor.com/uploads/1/2/0/2/12023481/798083717.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.calculushumor.com%2Fuploads%2F1%2F2%2F0%2F2%2F12023481%2F798083717.png&h=c3286bce&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n數學係科學之母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係，數學只係描述科學既工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你數學學唔好<br />\n係咪會影響你理解科學呀？</blockquote><br />\n係，但唔代表數學係科學之母"},{"pid":"73376f505d85d95e758991265d9d284382a71c3f","tid":401394,"uid":34892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:49:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://www.calculushumor.com/uploads/1/2/0/2/12023481/798083717.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.calculushumor.com%2Fuploads%2F1%2F2%2F0%2F2%2F12023481%2F798083717.png&h=c3286bce&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n數學係科學之母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係，數學只係描述科學既工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁冇數學邊有科學啊</blockquote><br />\n冇數學絕對有科學，科學係描述緊現實世界，就算冇數學存在都可以做到<br />\n當然，我認同數學對科學係好重要，因為佢提供左一種方法去幫我地描述現實世界，現代科學亦離唔開數學<br />\n但唔代表數學係科學之母，更唔代表冇數學就冇科學</blockquote><br />\n你講得啱，冇數學係可以有科學<br />\nHypothesis -&gt; Experimental Verification -&gt; theory 呢啲科學解釋嘅步驟都唔一定有數學成份<br />\n但一定唔係依家呢個世界見到精準嘅現代科學。<br />\n你知道我哋現代科學答緊嘅問題唔係剩係有冇現象發生，<br />\n而通常都係量化嘅問題，例如萬有引力有幾大，咩時間會發生，有咩嘢時空上嘅限制。"},{"pid":"64b43bdba353bcc765d9b1d44489001a88bf4502","tid":401394,"uid":34892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:52:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://www.calculushumor.com/uploads/1/2/0/2/12023481/798083717.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.calculushumor.com%2Fuploads%2F1%2F2%2F0%2F2%2F12023481%2F798083717.png&h=c3286bce&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n數學係科學之母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係，數學只係描述科學既工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁冇數學邊有科學啊</blockquote><br />\n冇數學絕對有科學，科學係描述緊現實世界，就算冇數學存在都可以做到<br />\n當然，我認同數學對科學係好重要，因為佢提供左一種方法去幫我地描述現實世界，現代科學亦離唔開數學<br />\n但唔代表數學係科學之母，更唔代表冇數學就冇科學</blockquote><br />\n你講得啱，冇數學係可以有科學<br />\nHypothesis -&gt; Experimental Verification -&gt; theory 呢啲科學解釋嘅步驟都唔一定有數學成份<br />\n但一定唔係依家呢個世界見到精準嘅現代科學。<br />\n你知道我哋現代科學答緊嘅問題唔係剩係有冇現象發生，<br />\n而通常都係量化嘅問題，例如萬有引力有幾大，咩時間會發生，有咩嘢時空上嘅限制。</blockquote><br />\n而解答量化嘅問題當然需要數學模型啦。"},{"pid":"ccf0f1d91fae03e708e96ddee4f8eb5c23ab46c0","tid":401394,"uid":34892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:52:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://www.calculushumor.com/uploads/1/2/0/2/12023481/798083717.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.calculushumor.com%2Fuploads%2F1%2F2%2F0%2F2%2F12023481%2F798083717.png&h=c3286bce&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n數學係科學之母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係，數學只係描述科學既工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>